result.execSummary:
The defendant Justin L. Douglas was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case.

  • 1st Degree Child Sex Assault - Sexual Contact with Person under Age of 13 [Modifiers: Repeater], a class B felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.02(1)(e).
  • Child Sexual Exploitation-Employ,Use,Induce [Modifiers: Repeater], a class C felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.05(1)(a).
  • Child Sexual Exploitation - Videos, Records, etc. [Modifiers: Repeater], a class C felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.05(1)(b).
  • Possession of Child Pornography [Modifiers: Repeater], a class D felony, Wisconsin Statutes 948.12(1m).
  • Bail Jumping-Felony [Modifiers: Repeater], a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(b).

superMiscConds.notes: Court waives costs. The Defendant is to abide by all rules and conditions of the Agent. The Defendant is to maintain absolute sobriety - no alcohol or drugs unless prescribed by a physician. The Defendant is to have no contact with the victims in this case. The Defendant is not to possess cell phones, computers, or camera devices.
